title: Another case of beautiful spaghetti code

embed.description: How does Rito fuck up this bad.. still? Don't worry gents, we won the game

body:
Hey summoners

I'm sure you've all seen this happen once before (mostly on social media), this happened in my game just yesterday, I thought it was amazing to witness something so explainable. 
Personally I hope Riot gets around to fixing this along with ADC's.
Don't worry though, we still won {{champion:17}} 

~Rexisea
